Package org.opt4j.benchmarks.knapsack

package org.opt4j.benchmarks.knapsack
Provides the classes for the knapsack benchmark. See "E. Zitzler and L. Thiele: Multiobjective evolutionary algorithms: A comparative case study and the strength Pareto approach. IEEE Transactions on Evolutionary Computation, vol. 3, no. 4, pp. 257-271, Nov. 1999." .
